Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.36,0:00:02.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Remember...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.92,0:00:04.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}But doctor, I remember everything.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.88,0:00:07.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}People forget things\Nwhen they have Alzheimer's.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.08,0:00:09.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}But sooner or later,\NI will forget things, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.00,0:00:13.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}All my memories, experiences\Nwill be erased, they will go away.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.08,0:00:15.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}What will happen to me?\NWhat will happen to my personality?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.80,0:00:18.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Our peaceful, sweet Agah\Nscolding the waiter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.76,0:00:21.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.24,0:00:23.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I chose you from 50 girls.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}It wasn't because your father was a cop.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.32,0:00:29.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}How does it feel\Nto be the only woman
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.40,0:00:32.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}working in an homicide bureau\Nwith 140 staff members?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.44,0:00:34.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I've never felt so good.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.40,0:00:36.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Dad, I'm getting a divorce.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.36,0:00:40.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}It's over, I can't tolerate this man no\Nmore. We are moving back with Deva.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.28,0:00:43.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I'm not doing anything, Naimhan.\NI haven't done anything.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.12,0:00:44.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}You did it. You and them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.92,0:00:45.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}All of you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.68,0:02:43.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Nevra, why did you bother\Nto come here?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.16,0:02:44.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}We could come to you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Where do you know me from?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.28,0:02:53.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Who doesn't know you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.64,0:02:54.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}You're famous.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.48,0:02:57.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Anyway.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}What's up? What's the matter?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.32,0:03:03.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}If it's within our power,\Nwe'll take care of it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.28,0:03:08.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}You'll get cancer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.00,0:03:24.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Why did you set fire\Nto the courthouse?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I didn't do it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}You were arrested.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.24,0:03:32.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Give a dog a bad name.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.52,0:03:36.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I'll beat the rap in the first session,\NI'm waiting for it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I know you are,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}but you have set fire to it before.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Seven years ago.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.08,0:03:48.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}That's different. I served my time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.76,0:03:57.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Do you know this man?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Look closely.\NHis file was in that building.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}They saw his case there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Don't know him. Never seen him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.76,0:04:20.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}What did this man do?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Killed a judge.\N- Damn.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I thought about it once,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.40,0:04:34.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}but then I said, never mind.\NIt's not worth it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Didn't do it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.16,0:04:39.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}But you set fire to the courthouse\Nwhere you worked as a bailiff.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.96,0:04:41.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}It's a courthouse, love.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.20,0:04:45.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}It burns, floods, even collapses.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.04,0:04:47.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Evidence gets lost.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.84,0:04:49.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Case files fly away.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.04,0:04:51.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Let me tell you something, love.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}They must have found\Na wretched man like me,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.60,0:05:00.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}gave him some money,\Nso he sparked a match.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Look, love.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}My town is famous for two things.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.16,0:05:19.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}The blackest of grape,\Nand the darkest of man.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.88,0:05:29.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}That building burns down\Nevery five or ten years, see?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.76,0:05:34.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Let's see if you can find the person who\Nhired the arsonist, if you have the balls.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Then you'll find out.\NI'll be shouting in front of the building.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.64,0:05:40.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}But they'll all be free\Nbefore I finish my words!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}And you'll be alone, too!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.32,0:05:46.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}The defendant, Nevra Elmas!\NThe plaintiff, Nevra Elmas!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}See how you like that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.04,0:06:03.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- What are you doing?\N- You're up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.40,0:06:05.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}But why did you leave your bed?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.00,0:06:07.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}And you took out your IV needle.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.04,0:06:09.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Come here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.00,0:06:12.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}We must alert the nurses.\NThey told us to call when you woke up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.96,0:06:14.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Where's the car?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- What car?\N- My car, of course. Where is it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.00,0:06:26.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}A tow truck removed it.\NThey gave us an address.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}The police gave mom\Na piece of paper with the address.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.76,0:06:31.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Pick up that paper. We'll get the car.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Now?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}But you just left intensive care.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.88,0:06:38.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}They took you to a room, and you almost\Nregained your consciousness.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.60,0:06:42.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- So?\N- You mumbled something but we didn't hear.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.16,0:06:43.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}How? What did I say?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.04,0:06:47.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}A cat named Munir or something.\NYou asked about him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- You asked if we fed him.\N- Huh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.00,0:06:53.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Grandpa. Don't you remember anything?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.36,0:06:57.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}How you came to the hospital?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.00,0:06:59.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}You had an angiogram.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.12,0:07:03.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I remember. I remember everything.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.32,0:07:06.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Come, let's get the car.\N- What will you do with it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.16,0:07:09.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I can't leave the car there.\NIt's a memento from Mebrure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}That's your grandma's car. Come on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.76,0:07:15.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Slowly. This way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- There goes my head again.\N- Evening, sir.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.88,0:07:25.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Good evening, son.\NTake me slowly.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.84,0:07:29.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Okay. What's wrong?\N- My head's spinning.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.16,0:07:32.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}The doctor says walk,\Nbut what good is walking?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.28,0:07:34.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Your slippers...\NWhere are we going?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- We'll get the keys.\N- Grandpa...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Dad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.20,0:09:25.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Dad, are you awake?\NI'll alert the nurses.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.72,0:09:28.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- No, mom. The nurses know.\N- They do?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.48,0:09:31.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}They told him to rest.\NThe doctor will see him tomorrow.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.16,0:09:33.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I'm all right, sweetie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.88,0:09:36.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}You gave us such a scare.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.24,0:09:41.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}What were you doing there\Nat that time of night?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}On the other side of the city.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}You left the house,\Nand didn't tell us anything.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.04,0:09:49.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Where were you going?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.92,0:09:57.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I don't know how to tell you this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.36,0:10:03.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I wish I could have said\Nbefore... Somehow.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.28,0:10:07.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}You have the right to know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.40,0:10:12.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}People sometimes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.84,0:10:16.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}go into a wholly different mood.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.68,0:10:22.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}They do things\Nthey wouldn't dream of.
