Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.64,0:21:02.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}In conclusion,\Nhe told me to do what I must.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.24,0:21:04.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Do you know what this means?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.96,0:21:08.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}If the Nevra\Nthis killer is talking about...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.40,0:21:13.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}is the same Nevra\Nsitting across the table right now,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.12,0:21:16.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}and you learn about this,\Nand don't tell me,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}you can't be a police anymore.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.44,0:21:23.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Understood, Chief.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.44,0:21:25.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Good.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.48,0:21:27.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Good.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.56,0:21:29.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.60,0:21:33.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Thank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.40,0:21:52.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I have an idea.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.96,0:22:02.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I'm going mad.\NI'm about to lose my mind.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.12,0:22:03.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Where is this man?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.48,0:22:06.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}He left his phone, too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.16,0:22:07.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}He doesn't use it, anyway.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.84,0:22:13.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}What's this book\Nhe asked you to buy so urgently?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.28,0:22:14.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}No idea.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.68,0:22:16.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Life Is Traffic, by Nukhet Coban.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.72,0:22:30.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Hi. This is Agah's room, isn't it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.76,0:22:32.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Agah, my boy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.24,0:22:35.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}What are you up to now?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.48,0:22:42.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Our department had this guy, Zekai.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.20,0:22:43.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Such a sweet man.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.68,0:22:45.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}He had a son\Nwho caught pneumonia.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.04,0:22:47.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Very severe.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.40,0:22:51.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Doctors said he wouldn't live.\NWhat could Zekai do?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.44,0:22:52.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}He lost all hope on doctors.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.36,0:22:55.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}He visited holy sepulchers,\Nmade offerings.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.56,0:23:02.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}The boy they said would die,\Nmiraculously recovered.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.36,0:23:06.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Zekai, of course,\Nwent to make his offering.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.04,0:23:12.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}He's made a vow\Nto make nine paupers happy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.84,0:23:16.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Because his son was nine. Whatever...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.20,0:23:19.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}He goes to a poor neighborhood.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.68,0:23:21.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}His money's ready.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.80,0:23:23.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}He gives the money away.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.12,0:23:26.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Makes nine paupers happy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.08,0:23:33.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}A tenth pauper appears.\N"I'm poor, too." he says.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.72,0:23:37.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Zekai says he's out of money,\Nbut the guy won't believe him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.92,0:23:42.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}"You gave a fortune away,\Nwhere's mine?" he asks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.16,0:23:46.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- And stabs Zekai.\N- Oh, dear.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.64,0:23:48.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Such a pity.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.16,0:23:49.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.88,0:23:54.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}But then, you understand the tenth pauper.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.36,0:23:56.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Sure, sure.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.72,0:23:59.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}You give money to everybody,\Nand when it's his turn...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.12,0:24:03.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}This happens sometimes. I mean...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.96,0:24:05.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}There's a crime, but not a criminal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.04,0:24:07.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Hello there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.48,0:24:11.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Agah, sir? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.80,0:24:14.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Why?\N- Everyone's looking for you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.40,0:24:25.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Has Zuhal left?\N- Who?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.76,0:24:30.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- I'll go.\N- Were you staying here?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.76,0:24:34.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Agah, visit me some time!\N- Like hell I will. It's your fault.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.72,0:24:45.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Hello, Ates? Can you talk?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.48,0:24:50.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Yeah, I'm at work. At the department.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.92,0:24:54.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}There's this thing. Urgent.\NCould you come here?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.48,0:25:01.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Nothing to worry about.\NCome. I'm waiting.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.96,0:25:50.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Sorry. I had a thing.\N- I'm sorry I couldn't come.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:50.44,0:25:52.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}To your department, I mean.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.24,0:25:55.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}They don't like me over there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:57.04,0:25:58.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}It's as close as I can get.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.08,0:26:02.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}This is for you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.48,0:26:04.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Thanks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.88,0:26:07.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}It's cold, though.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:09.12,0:26:10.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I was like this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.00,0:26:13.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Workaholic.\NCoffees went cold all the time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:15.08,0:26:17.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I may not look like it but I used to be
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:18.24,0:26:21.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}a fiery and an idealist reporter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:21.72,0:26:23.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I was a police reporter, too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:24.04,0:26:25.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I don't about the fire,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:25.48,0:26:27.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}but there's still some idealism left.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:28.36,0:26:30.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Otherwise why would you come\Nall this way, no?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.00,0:26:34.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Maybe I just wanted to see you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:34.16,0:26:35.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Why not?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:36.56,0:26:40.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Maybe it's two birds\Nwith one stone. Why not?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.64,0:26:42.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Never.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:45.04,0:26:47.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}As I am still carrying that idealism,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:49.56,0:26:52.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I am also carrying a stone\Nfor each bird.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.08,0:27:01.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- What's this?\N- It's a story.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:02.16,0:27:03.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Can you publish it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:06.48,0:27:08.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}"An anonymous law enforcement source."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:09.56,0:27:11.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Exactly that.\N- Hmm.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:12.36,0:27:15.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I gave you this. You're giving it back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:17.60,0:27:19.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}To me, that's romantic.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:22.32,0:27:24.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- The sooner the better.\N- All right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:25.80,0:27:27.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I'll post it online.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:29.24,0:27:30.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Had a look at the courthouse yet?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:31.00,0:27:32.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I did, but it's a dead end.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:39.80,0:27:42.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Then I could send you\Nto an entirely different street.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:43.28,0:27:45.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Your dead judge...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:45.84,0:27:48.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}All his cases\Ninvolved some sort of bribery.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:48.96,0:27:50.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Public knowledge, too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:50.36,0:27:52.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Might as well have invoiced them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:53.12,0:27:54.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}If you were to look at...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:55.56,0:27:58.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}whose lives he'd ruined in those cases,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:58.68,0:28:00.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}maybe you'll find something.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:02.92,0:28:04.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}But his record is spotless.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:08.04,0:28:12.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Then for one time only,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:12.80,0:28:14.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}he didn't take a bribe...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:15.48,0:28:17.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}But gave a bribe.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:22.24,0:28:25.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Use your other medicine.\NThey won't cause a problem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:26.08,0:28:29.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}But sir, you have to\Nlet your daughter know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:29.60,0:28:31.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:32.28,0:28:34.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I must accept it first.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:34.28,0:28:36.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Then I'll tell them both.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:36.64,0:28:38.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Alzheimer's is a serious condition.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:40.72,0:28:43.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Tailor-made for a serious man like myself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:44.84,0:28:46.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Where were you this morning?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:46.32,0:28:47.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Your daughter worried about you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:49.40,0:28:51.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}The night I had a heart attack,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:52.60,0:28:54.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I had a sharp pain right here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.72,0:28:58.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I said, "Agah, this is it.\NYou're leaving this life."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:00.36,0:29:02.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}First thing I thought about
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:02.80,0:29:05.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}was what my daughter\Nand grandson was going to do.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:06.44,0:29:07.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}What would become of them?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:09.04,0:29:11.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}So interesting.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:12.12,0:29:15.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}So long as man doesn't understand\Nthat he's dying,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:15.76,0:29:19.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}he doesn't think about\Nthose he's leaving behind.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:19.12,0:29:20.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I called my lawyer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:21.28,0:29:23.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Told him to leave them everything.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:23.40,0:29:25.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}They shouldn't have to deal\Nwith the inheritance stuff.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:25.76,0:29:28.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I was busy with those things.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:28.16,0:29:30.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I didn't want to make them sad,\Nand didn't tell them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:33.48,0:29:34.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Come in, please.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:38.12,0:29:40.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Let's get to the point.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:40.60,0:29:43.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}You'll be our guest for another day.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:43.08,0:29:45.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Okay?\N- Okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:46.00,0:29:48.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- All right. Get well soon.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:54.12,0:29:55.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}You made us leave.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:55.76,0:29:57.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I couldn't ask while he's here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:57.84,0:30:00.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}What's this thing\Nyou can't share with us?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:02.64,0:30:05.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}You know about\Nthe heart attack I had, sweetie?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:07.20,0:30:11.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I asked the doctor about\Nmy sexual life this point on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:12.44,0:30:13.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Now you know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:14.48,0:30:16.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Would you have liked to listen?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:22.68,0:30:24.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I wish I could stay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:25.00,0:30:27.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}No, you go home and rest.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:27.68,0:30:29.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}We'll be back tomorrow anyway.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:29.68,0:30:30.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Dad called today.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:32.60,0:30:34.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Finally, huh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:34.80,0:30:37.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Finally he must've understand\Nwhat he's done.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:38.32,0:30:40.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Doesn't have the face\Nto call me, either.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:40.48,0:30:42.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}So he called you.\NWhat is he saying?
