Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:48.08,0:30:49.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Ah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:49.84,0:30:51.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}That's a relief.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:51.68,0:30:52.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Really. I'm relieved.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:53.60,0:30:55.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I mean...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:55.84,0:30:57.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}That's a load off my shoulder.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:57.56,0:30:58.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I'm happy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:59.24,0:31:00.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}So happy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:00.60,0:31:02.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Finally, that's done.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:04.40,0:31:07.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Mom, you're fine, right?\N- Why wouldn't I be?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:52.76,0:32:54.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Good night.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:09.00,0:33:10.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}That's not me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:11.20,0:33:12.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}It's some other Nevra Elmas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:14.48,0:33:16.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Or like Firuz had said,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:16.16,0:33:19.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}he must have seen me on TV\Nor the newspaper, and is addressing me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:23.04,0:33:25.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}That may be.\NBut the real question is
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:25.76,0:33:28.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}not whom he's writing,\Nbut why he's writing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:28.80,0:33:30.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I think he's alone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:30.32,0:33:33.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Crippling from it, in fact.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:33.44,0:33:34.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}No one to speak with.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:35.88,0:33:38.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Even if he does, nobody's listening.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:39.28,0:33:41.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}He wants to be\Nlistened to so badly,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:42.32,0:33:44.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}he's willing to kill for it.
