Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:55.72,0:33:57.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Who could be that lonely?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:25.16,0:34:27.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Zuhal? Darling?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:04.24,0:37:06.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Mister? Mister?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:08.84,0:37:10.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Are you okay, mister?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:16.04,0:37:18.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Peace be with you.\N- And also with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:18.96,0:37:20.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}What brought you here, at this hour?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:20.92,0:37:23.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I've come to take my car.\NThey towed it here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:23.40,0:37:24.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Come tomorrow.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:25.00,0:37:27.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}No. Tomorrow won't do.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:27.12,0:37:29.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I'm coming from the hospital.\NI have somebody sick.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:29.48,0:37:32.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I have to take the car there,\Nand go to their hometown.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:32.60,0:37:35.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I wish them well.\NWhere are you from?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:40.84,0:37:44.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Mister. Are you feeling better?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:45.00,0:37:47.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}We've called an ambulance.\NThey'll be here soon.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:48.76,0:37:49.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:50.80,0:37:51.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}What are you saying?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:51.88,0:37:53.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- In the car.\N- What's there?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:57.00,0:37:58.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}In the bag...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:58.20,0:37:59.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- What's there?\N- In the bag...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:05.84,0:38:07.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Mister...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:08.44,0:38:10.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Mister.\N- In the car...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:10.20,0:38:11.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- What?\N- My car.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:44.52,0:39:47.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}This second murder is really\Nmaking national headlines.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:49.52,0:39:53.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}While the nationwide search for the\Nkiller, Tufan Elibol, is still ongoing,
