Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:00.60,0:40:05.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}According to the anonymous\Nlaw enforcement source,
