Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:09.80,0:40:13.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Indeed, dear viewers,\Nhe may be a victim of them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:01.76,0:41:02.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Hey!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:06.80,0:41:08.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}You sissy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:10.20,0:41:13.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I'll make you pay for this!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:27.60,0:41:31.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Bloody hell. Hey!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:42.48,0:41:43.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Screw this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:46.92,0:43:48.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Fuck! Fuck this!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:00.92,0:44:03.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Help!\N- What are you doing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:05.08,0:44:08.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}What are you doing?\NYou'll break the elevator.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:10.08,0:44:12.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Stop it.\N- Help!
