Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:20.88,0:44:22.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Help me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:23.52,0:44:26.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}What are you doing?\NWhy are you yelling for nothing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:26.96,0:44:29.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Open it.\NI can't hear you, open this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:31.40,0:44:35.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Sir, I beg you. Let me go,\NI won't go to the police.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:35.12,0:44:38.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- I'll go home.\N- Okay. That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:38.68,0:44:40.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- I beg you, sir.\N- If you'll let me finish...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:40.96,0:44:43.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}- Just...\N- I... Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:47.60,0:44:48.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Now...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:49.24,0:44:50.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}The mechanic says...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:51.60,0:44:54.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}When the elevator is stuck\Nbetween two floors,
