Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:57.32,0:44:58.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}If it doesn't move,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:59.36,0:45:02.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}it's something only\Nthe mechanic could fix.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:04.84,0:45:06.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}I can't kill you here.
