Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:08.96,0:45:13.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}Help me! Help!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:20.04,0:45:23.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i0\bord1\3c&H0}{\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI}{\an2}So, let me tell you how we'll do this.
